text: A Twelve-Year Night () is a 2018 Uruguayan Spanish Argentine French German drama movie directed by Álvaro Brechner and starring Antonio de la Torre, Chino Darín, Alfonso Tort, César Troncoso, Soledad Villamil. ==Other websites== * Category:2018 drama movies Category:Uruguayan movies Category:Spanish drama movies Category:Argentine drama movies Category:French drama movies Category:German drama movies Category:Movies directed by Álvaro Brechner
